<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <p>
      tuṟai: centuṟaip pāṭāṇpāṭṭu, vaṇṇam: oḻukuvaṇṇam, tūkku: centūkku.
    </p>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Pati8.73">
        <l>uravō reṇṇiṉu maṭavō reṇṇiṉum</l>
        <l>piṟarkkunī yāyi ṉallatu niṉakkup</l>
        <l>piṟaruvama mākā voruperu vēntē </l>
        <l>polinta kūnta loṇṇutal polinta</l> <!-- taken from EFEO  -->
        <l>uyartiṇai makaḷir neñcattuc cēkkuṅ</l> <!-- taken from EFEO  -->
        <l>kurunteyvan tarūu <hi rend="bold">niṟantikaḻ pāciḻai</hi></l> <!-- taken from EFEO  -->
        <l>marutañ cāṉṟa malartalai viḷaivayaṟ </l>
        <l>ceyyu ṇārai yoyyu makaḷi </l>
        <l>riravum pakalum pāciḻai kaḷaiyār</l>
        <l>kuṟumpal yāṇark kuravai yayaruṅ</l>
        <l>kāviri maṇṭiya cēyviri vaṉappiṟ</l>
        <l>pukāarc celva pūḻiyar meymmaṟai</l>
        <l>kaḻaivirin teḻutaru maḻaitavaḻ neṭuṅkōṭṭuk</l>
        <l>kollip poruna koṭittērp poṟaiyaniṉ</l>
        <l>vaḷaṉu māṇmaiyuṅ kaivaṇ maiyu</l>
        <l>mānta raḷaviṟan taṉaveṉap paṉṉāḷ</l>
        <l>yāṉceṉ ṟuraippavun tēṟār piṟaruñ</l>
        <l>cāṉṟō ruraippat teḷikuvar kolleṉa</l>
        <l>vāṅkumati maruḷak kāṇkuval</l>
        <l>yāṅkuraip pēṉeṉa varuntuval yāṉē.</l>
        <!-- EW's main text: kūnta loṇṇutaṟ polinta makaḷir/ niṟantikaḻ yuyartiṇai makaḷir neñcattum/ kuṟunteyvan tarūu māṉṟōr; no source given -->
        <!-- EW's first suggestion AND R's second witness: (niṟantikaḻ pāciḻai) kūntal oṇṇutal polinta makaḷir niṟantikaḻ uyartiṇai makaḷir neñcattum, kuṟunteyvam tarūum āṉṟōr C4 -->
        <!-- EW's second suggestion is probably the same as EFEO, and adopted by R as her main text, see above   -->
        <!-- R's lemma in apparatus does NOT correspond to the main text: ...kūnta loṇṇutal polinta, niṟantikaḻ pāciḻai yuyartiṇai makaḷirum, teyvan tarūu neñcat tāṉṟōr EV, ER  -->
        <!-- R's first witness is EFEO, but she leaves out chunks, so this should be checked: polinta kūnta loṇṇutal ….. …. niṟantikaḻ pāciḻai EFEO  -->
        <!-- R's second witness is the same as EW's first suggestion: (niṟantikaḻ pāciḻai) kūntal oṇṇutal polinta makaḷir niṟantikaḻ uyartiṇai makaḷir neñcattum , kuṟunteyvam tarūum āṉṟōr C4 -->
        <!-- What SEA has done here: main text: EFEO, lemma: EFEO, witnesses: editions and C4; what still needs to be added: EC and other mss witnesses even when the omit these 3 lines  -->
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
        <l></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>

